entries.femaleVariant: Hey, no firing at civilians!
Careful! They're just workers, for chrissake!
You won't blow it open that way!
Let's help the others first. That gate's not going anywhere.
Right as rain. OK, it's our turn now.
V – watch them, all right?
Copy that.
I got a terminal. We're jacking in.
What about security protocols?
V, it's not a space station, it's a dumb, big-ass drill.
Don't worry. Carol will slice through it like butter.
Watch out! Coming from the right!
How are we doing, Mitch?
Eleven percent!
Shit. Can't you speed it up?
Our hands are tied.
Dammit, left side too!
Whoever's closest, deal with them!
Carol? Mitch? How much longer?
Twenty-seven percent.
Guess that's all of 'em.
There's likely a control room upstairs. We can link remotely to the SERC from there.
Damn, it’s lookin' like the drill vector's on auto.
How can we possibly turn it?
We gonna sweet-talk this bitch into it. Mitch, kill that autopilot and hit manual override.
Got it. It's working!
Prepare for takeoff.
We've got company!
A lot of it, too.
Fuck. How much longer up there?!
Almost there! Nearly at sixty percent!
What do you mean? We keep going! Finish this!
What now?
We're in!
Move, move!
AV! Goddamn AV inbound!
It's like they've sent a small army against us.
They're going to land!
Everybody ready!
Just as I thought – a whole squad coming at us!
Teddy, get the hell out of there!
Teddy!
Oh my lord!
Things are about to get real ugly.
I have eyes on the fuckers. Mitch?
Listen, we just hit Night Corp ICE. Carol's cutting through. It's slow work, but it'll get done. Where are you all at?
I got him! Direct hit!
He's out of our hair! Shit, V, we might actually pull this off!
How do you like that, Milishits?!
Holy shit. We did it! They're smoldering wrecks! We did that!
We're moving on. We'll try to buy you as much time as we can.
Much obliged. We'll keep watch over Mitch and Carol and see to that gate.
So, Panam? Gonna show 'em what this lump of scrap can do?
We're hit!
Fuck! We can't hold out much longer!
They're tearing us to shreds!
V, we've taken hard hits, too hard! Everything here's hanging by a thread and sheer will!
The gate is planted firm in the land and secured tight. We're trying to figure out where to place the charges, but we need more time!
There's no thumb-twiddling going on here! We'll buy you as much time as we can! Hang in there!
Saul, Mitch, headin' back your way.
We're on our way.
I'm wondering if I really believed… believed we'd make it through.
After that display, you can be sure there's a place for you in the panzerboy ranks!
Impressive, V. Thanks.
Now, if you don't mind – there's a monster gate that needs to be blown open.
V, get back to the panzer! We don't have time!
V, she's dying, like I said she would. Propulsion, weapons systems, launchers – all falling like dominoes!
[Get out] We'll provide cover, just hurry!
I can't believe it, but I think it worked! The lump of scrap's still got some life in her! Systems are lighting up. We're back!
We'll provide cover. Just hurry, all right?!
You get out. Help our folks!
Panam, how much longer?!
Uh, listen, this party is spinning out of control! Militech is sending tanks our way!
Coming down the road. I've got the drone watching them! It's a damned combat unit!
I'm doing my best! Mitch, do you read? The navigation module is jamming the other systems. Can I cut it?
Inside, V, quick!
I'm doing what I can, Saul! It's not like Mitch is here, Bobby's dead...! I'm by my fucking self here!
I'll try. Either I do this, or this rattle trap will really be scrap!
There anything you can do about it?
Their position?
We won't stand a chance without the panzer. Panam?
Yes! Cut it! She'll be fine without it!
I know, Panam. I know. We'll keep you covered.
Thank you.
If those Militch tanks reach us, they'll roll us flat like so many roaches.
Stop thinkin' about the tanks, consider 'em gone. You blast open that gate.
Are you two all right?
Those aren't standard issue armor... What the hell are they?
The latest models, just off Militech's assembly line.
Be careful, all right? We don't want any more casulaties.
Mitch would never forgive me if I let them bust her up. Let's give 'em hell.
Shit's about to get biblical…
Good work. But we've got a minor hitch here.
What is it?
Raggedy-ass system spat us out. And no hard-reset didn't help. We pretty much outta options, here.
Hot-wiring the SERC on location – that seems our one option, now.
It could have been worse. What about the gate?
The blasts shook the foundations, but it won't yield without the panzer's help. We need you for the finishing touch.
And… I don't know. It's as if my brain was on autopilot the whole time.
We're past the worst of this storm, there's that.
Knew we'd make it, whole time.
Don't jinx this.
Honestly, doubted we'd make it.
Knew the whole time we'd make it. Felt it in my bones.
Honestly? Thought we'd be maggot-meat by now.
Don't jinx it! Not now.
Someday you will have to tell me how you came to be so damned cocksure about everything.
It's just not fair.
You saw those tanks. You an' me still breathin's a minor miracle.
If anyone ought to believe in miracles, V, it's you.
Oh, stop. The odds had us face down in the mud long past. But we beat them. We have the right to be pleased.
OK, let's move on quick. Militech's bit down, they won't let go. Support's likely on the way.
All right. We're firing up the SERC, aiming to bore through to Arasaka Tower. This will take some time.
V! Militech's throwing more armor at us! By the ton!
V, help us out, here! Fucking Militech is not letting up!
God damned corpos! More company incoming!
Oh my, that's what I call a true whoomp. Mitch, is everything all right?
We'll handle them.
Impressive rumble, yeah, but all seems good.
V, we'll need you to cover us!
Get your ass moving our way, fast!
The Militech armor – we have to intercept. Before it reaches the others.
Mhm. They're done and gone.
